title: ►OPEN HOME THURSDAY ►REMODELED FLAT!
posting_body: ['OPEN HOME:', 'THURSDAY, AUGUST 4, FROM 5:30 P.M. TO 5:45 P.M.', 'Please reply by email to this posting if you would like to attend.', 'A confirmed appointment is required to view this home.', 'KEY DETAILS:', '•Bedrooms: 2 Bedrooms', '•Bathrooms: 1 Bathroom', '•Property Type: Apartment', '•Lease Duration: Long-term or short-term - 1 Year Preferred', '•Pets Policy: Pets Welcome', '•Laundry: Washer and Dryer in unit', '•Walk Score: 99 - Transit Score: 93 - Bike Score: 99', 'Meticulously Renovated Victorian flat in a 6-unit building with a highly desirable open floor plan in the heart of Inner Mission.', "This unit boasts high ceilings, all hardwood (pergo) floors, 2-bedrooms, a gorgeous, remodeled chef's kitchen, a beautifully finished bathroom, and a rarely found-in-unit washer and dryer.", 'Useful bike racks and secured storage complement this home.', 'Valencia Street Gourmet Ghetto resides just a few blocks away, with supermarkets, shops, hip cafes, restaurants, convenient public transportation, and BART.', 'This home is a commuter dream with easy access to 101/280 freeways, ample street parking, a public parking lot with low monthly rates, and Getaround (car sharing) within half a block.', 'Walk Score: 99 - Transit Score: 93 - Bike Score: 99', 'About you:', '1.', 'Clean credit.', '2.', "First-month rent and a security deposit of one month's rent.", '3.', 'The lease is for one year, but the term is fully negotiable.', '4.', 'The move-in date is anytime in August or September 1st.', 'Thank you for reading this posting.', 'If you would like to attend the showing, please reply by email to this posting, and I will forward the address to you.', 'All home showings are by confirmed appointment.']
